<h3>How time and activities affect your condition</h3>

<p>Tell us about things that make your condition worse or better. What helps? What doesn't help?</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <th>Name</th>
    <% human_keys(RecordsThing.scores.keys).each do |score_hash| %>
      <th><%= score_hash.first %></th>
    <% end %>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% Thing.all.each do |thing| %>
      <%= render 'records_things/form', thing: thing %>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<%= hidden_field_tag :record_id, value: @record.id %>
<%= submit_tag "Save" %>
